	<a href='http://www.bakertilly.co.uk'>Home</a> <span class="separator">&rsaquo;</span> <a href="/publications/Pages/publicationsandviews.aspx">Publications and views</a> <span class="separator">&rsaquo;</span> <a href="/publications/taxplanningbulletin/Pages/Tax-planning-bulletin.aspx">Tax Planning Bulletin</a> <span class="separator">&rsaquo;</span> <span class='current'>50% tax rate and possible rise in capital gains tax</span>
